#: /var/home/joshuaroman/plasmallm/package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:691
msgid ""
"WARNING: When combined with Auto-share, enables agentic workflow. Only use "
"with very trustworthy LLMs."
msgstr ""
"ADVERTENCIA: Combinado con Auto-compartir, habilita el flujo de trabajo "
"agéntico. Usar solo con LLMs muy confiables."

#: /var/home/joshuaroman/plasmallm/package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:698
